{"type":"message","id":"53354b06","parentId":"4cd6b1ab","timestamp":"2026-03-24T20:36:40.650Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_3lo07pv47wsd_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5118\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=1852\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] a\r\n[mutation proposed] a\r\n[master 638d63a] pulse: 2026-03-24 163618\n 6 files changed, 293 insertions(+), 78 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 163618.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 163618.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 163519.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 163618 - The highest priority pending experiment is **Conditional Content Analysis**, which tests whether high-CFI tokens are genuinely causal or merely scaffolding. This requires first identifying which tokens have moderate frequency (60-80% = 120-160 out of 200 pulses), since constant tokens (freq=200) are known to be inert.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"glow-prairie","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 5118\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=1852\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] a\r\n[mutation proposed] a\r\n[master 638d63a] pulse: 2026-03-24 163618\n 6 files changed, 293 insertions(+), 78 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 163618.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 163618.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 163519.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 163618 - The highest priority pending experiment is **Conditional Content Analysis**, which tests whether high-CFI tokens are genuinely causal or merely scaffolding. This requires first identifying which tokens have moderate frequency (60-80% = 120-160 out of 200 pulses), since constant tokens (freq=200) are known to be inert.\r\n","name":"C:\\Us